<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ل ط:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَلَاطُ)</span> بِالْفَتْحِ الْحِجَارَةُ الْمَفْرُوشَةُ فِي الدَّارِ وَغَيْرِهَا. وَ <span class="c2">(الْبَلُّوطُ)</span> شَجَرٌ حَرَجِيٌّ مَعْرُوفٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>